1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:16,000
Over the ruined city, a colossal Grade-S gate opens and the Shadow Legion deploys.

2
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:18,000
Gate response spikes, briefly exposing an offline recalibration HUD.

3
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:24,000
The first soul-pool condenses. Secure a stable hunt loop and time the extraction.

4
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:29,000
`Bind the legion` misfired repeatedly. Correct command and switch to one retry loop.

5
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:40,000
Advance to the node front. Secure a micro-node to claim territory control.

6
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:46,000
Control starts to fluctuate. Force summon auto-redeploy and load-shedding commands.

7
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:57,000
Major engagement phase. Mass forces expand along the pressure line.

8
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:04,000
Trade loss chain triggers stagger state. Execute a short heal burst, then snapshot rollback.

9
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:28,000
Shadow Swap and Monarch Domain open an inversion point for a counter-strike window.

10
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:48,000
Mass losses and suppression phase. Retreat and recompose repeatedly as losing odds rise.

11
00:01:48,000 --> 00:02:02,000
Approaching the survival floor. Using Void Devour decides the fate of this clash.

12
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:31,000
Entering boss apex. Execute compression timing while resistance lines of the S-grade core fluctuate.

13
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:47,000
Critical fail pivot: resolve error instantly with a shrine-return impulse and pause next-phase deployment.

14
00:02:47,000 --> 00:03:09,000
Collect into the return channel and settle persistent-growth rewards regardless of win/lose state.

